<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= metaDescription %>" />
    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="<%= metaKeywords || '부동산 계산기, 부동산 커뮤니티, 공인중개사 시험' %>"
    />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= pageTitle %>" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= metaDescription %>" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= canonicalUrl || `${baseUrl}${currentPath}` %>" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= canonicalUrl || `${baseUrl}${currentPath}` %>" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <script defer src="/js/regionData.js"></script>
    <script defer src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <% if (includeCalculatorsScript) { %>
      <script defer src="/js/calculators.js"></script>
    <% } %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <span class="brand-badge">RE</span>
          <span>
            <strong>Real Estate Hub</strong>
            <small>Traffic + Community + SEO</small>
          </span>
        </a>

        <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="주요 메뉴">
          <a href="/" class="<%= currentPath === '/' ? 'is-active' : '' %>">홈</a>
          <a
            href="/calc"
            class="<%= currentPath.startsWith('/calc') ? 'is-active' : '' %>"
          >
            계산기
          </a>
          <a
            href="/community"
            class="<%= currentPath.startsWith('/community') ? 'is-active' : '' %>"
          >
            커뮤니티
          </a>
          <a
            href="/exam"
            class="<%= currentPath.startsWith('/exam') ? 'is-active' : '' %>"
          >
            시험 정보
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="site-main">
      <%- include(bodyView) %>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="container footer-grid">
        <div>
          <h2>Real Estate Hub</h2>
          <p>
            부동산 계산기, 커뮤니티, 공인중개사 시험 정보를 중심으로 검색 유입과
            재방문을 만드는 수익형 플랫폼입니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>핵심 카테고리</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/calc">부동산 계산기</a></li>
            <li><a href="/community">부동산 커뮤니티</a></li>
            <li><a href="/exam">공인중개사 시험 정보</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>AdSense 준비 영역</h2>
          <div class="ad-slot ad-slot-footer">
            <span>Footer AdSense Placeholder</span>
            <small>실제 승인 후 광고 코드를 삽입하세요.</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Real Estate Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
